queries.sql: SELECT SUM(quantidade * valor_unitario) as subtotal, SUM(valor_desconto) as total_desconto, SUM(valor_total) as total, COUNT(*) as quantidade_itens FROM `contrato_itens` WHERE `contrato_id` = 1 AND `contrato_itens`.`deleted_at` IS NULL LIMIT 1
